description:
Escape the ordinary with a truly beautiful collection of island wallpapers designed to fit your Veer or Pixi!

Who has time to sift through thousands of so-so images to find one good one to use as a background for your Veer? Pacific Island Wallpapers has 101 beautiful images from a tropical island in the Pacific. They are relaxing, interesting, and stunning! 
FEATURES
* 101 images of flowers, beaches, sunsets, birds, fish, and more from the island 
* Unique images you won't find anywhere else! 
* Set the image you are viewing to be the Veer wallpaper with one button press
* Can set an image as a wallpaper for Pixi phones
* Save any image to the wallpapers folder on your Veer (Not supported on Pixi phones)
* No resizing! All images are already the correct size for the Veer and Pixi.
* 7 categories make it easy to find the image you want 

Think you know what island this is? Go to k2techservice.com/forum to make a guess & see if you are correct.
